T1  - The CEO, venture capitalists, and the board
AU  - Rosenstein, Joseph
AU  - Bruno, Albert V.
AU  - Bygrave, William D.
AU  - Taylor, Natalie T.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 8
IS  - 2
SP  - 99
EP  - 113
